graph TB
    subgraph "MLflow Operator Component"
        Operator[MLflow Operator Controller]
        HelmChart[Embedded Helm Chart Engine]
        HTTPRouteCtrl[HTTPRoute Controller]
        ConsoleLinkCtrl[ConsoleLink Controller]

        Operator -->|renders templates| HelmChart
        Operator -->|reconciles| HTTPRouteCtrl
        Operator -->|reconciles| ConsoleLinkCtrl
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources per MLflow CR"
        MLflowServer[MLflow Server Pod<br/>Python App<br/>Port 8443/HTTPS]
        MLflowSvc[MLflow Service<br/>ClusterIP 8443/TCP]
        MLflowSA[ServiceAccount<br/>mlflow-sa]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>2Gi optional]
        TLSSecret[TLS Secret<br/>mlflow-tls]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Allow TCP/8443]
        HTTPRoute[HTTPRoute<br/>/mlflow prefix]
        ConsoleLink[ConsoleLink<br/>OpenShift Menu]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| MLflowCR[MLflow CR]
    MLflowCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates/updates| MLflowServer
    Operator -->|creates/updates| MLflowSvc
    Operator -->|creates/updates| MLflowSA
    Operator -->|creates/updates| PVC
    Operator -->|creates/updates| TLSSecret
    Operator -->|creates/updates| NetworkPolicy
    HTTPRouteCtrl -->|creates| HTTPRoute
    ConsoleLinkCtrl -->|creates| ConsoleLink

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        Gateway[data-science-gateway]
        OSConsole[OpenShift Console]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
    end

    Operator -->|watches/creates resources| K8sAPI
    HTTPRoute -->|routes traffic via| Gateway
    ConsoleLink -->|integrates with| OSConsole
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| Operator

    subgraph "Optional External Services"
        PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL Database<br/>Port 5432/TCP]
        S3[S3 Compatible Storage<br/>Port 443/HTTPS]
    end

    MLflowServer -.->|backend store<br/>optional| PostgreSQL
    MLflowServer -.->|artifact store<br/>optional| S3
    MLflowServer -->|auth checks| K8sAPI

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style MLflowServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MLflowCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Gateway fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PostgreSQL fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
